{"tid":485374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天津甲級商廈發生大火 至少6死5傷","createTime":"2017-12-01T02:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T05:28:52.000Z","uid":136994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e78a80fad9f72521a8703106d922a474d050a766","tid":485374,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171201/57526899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57526899&d=tM%2Bj00NxWG6U68T3aQiASwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f47aa58e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57526899&h=52d917eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171201/57526899</a><br />\n<br />\n天津河西區發生一宗奪命大火。事發於今日凌晨4時許，位於河西區友誼路與平江道交口城市大廈頂層38樓突然起火，消防部門和河西區委區政府趕赴現場處置。從相片可見，起火大廈的玻璃幕牆嚴重燒毀，部份窗戶燒剩焦黑的窗框。<br />\n<br />\n消防員拉喉將火救熄，事件中最少有11人送醫院救治，其中6人經搶救無效死亡。救援工作正在進行當中，起火原因正在進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n然而城市大廈的官方網頁資料，天津城市大廈隸屬於天津隆融置業，位處天津的金融中心友誼路，惟資料卻列出一楝36層的甲級寫子樓外，另有一楝36層服務式公寓，惟外界消息卻指起火點為大廈38樓，令事件蒙上神秘面紗，但有指該大廈沒有13及14樓。"},{"pid":"a80dda40cc65bb49db72b5853ce4f362deaba1c1","tid":485374,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"燒成炭，搵唔到唔算死"},{"pid":"acb6662fcd599040261e2f90500f73452e418891","tid":485374,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"清理低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4097c3a4cb75029e0e580b867412013dff8d42e","tid":485374,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清理低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人人有責"},{"pid":"9fce1d33d1307d633c6f3470464f31577000646a","tid":485374,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"天津又有燒雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab71c75573a75a88a551902bb5a9fe8b06b4daed","tid":485374,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JkwBhkA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJkwBhkA.gif&h=aea6778c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7d2e15bbaf460fa2b109bd4fa93f850ffd096e9","tid":485374,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"甲級低端, 抵燒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553b974f33f2a71f452393573297ed0f7baf15a1","tid":485374,"uid":47144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"支版911"},{"pid":"81facfed551a0155279a9d0667c802805b930017","tid":485374,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}